{"tid":52551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被劫大陸仔：香港治安麻麻","createTime":"2016-12-24T07:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T16:56:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":54,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f01de4500250d03c4c87a692c9e43ba7289bbf99","tid":52551,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"中國福建夫婦，昨日在港鐵上水站外行人天橋遇劫，被搶去約值400萬元的外幣﹝<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iaJETv﹞。事主目前留醫北區醫院，他聲稱巨款是「給朋友買樓用」，批評「香港治安麻麻地」。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iaJETv%EF%B9%9E%E3%80%82%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%A8%E6%AC%BE%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E7%B5%A6%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E7%94%A8%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B2%BB%E5%AE%89%E9%BA%BB%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%8D%E3%80%82&d=2Qb4jeYzGtvxSAJgkmDsQ5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3e83f664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iaJETv﹞。事主目前留醫北區醫院，他聲稱巨款是「給朋友買樓用」，批評「香港治安麻麻地」。</a><br />\n<br />\n遇劫的中國男子姓戚（39歲），目前留醫北區醫院的骨科病房，一臉疲態。對於是否涉及地下錢莊的工作，他拒絕回答，反說該400萬元全部是港幣，準備「給朋友買樓用」。他用廣東話稱，兇徒用刀斬他的腳，「根本追唔到」，同時批評「香港治安麻麻地」。他又表示，醫生指他的腳傷嚴重，至於康復後活動能力會否受影響，暫仍未知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161224&amp;guid=56087533&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161224%26guid%3D56087533%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=2Qb4jeYzGtvxSAJgkmDsQ5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7c6342cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161224%26guid%3D56087533%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=000adc25\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161224&amp;guid=56087533&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"52e22bc1528a28cfbeeb24fb56436f8405b7e978","tid":52551,"